title: Del Rio cross-country takes on Islander Splash meet
text: Courtesy Boys cross-country Del Rio’s varsity and junior varsity boys and girls cross-country teams took to the coast this weekend to compete in the Islander Splash in Corpus Christi. Courtesy Girls cross-country The varsity girls team finished seventh in its division, the varsity boys were 12th, the junior varsity girls were fourth and the junior varsity boys were 15th. Corpus Christi is also the site of this year’s regional meet. Posted: Sunday, September 27, 2015 1:00 am Del Rio cross-country takes on Islander Splash meet Brian Argabright Del Rio News-Herald | 0 comments Del Rio faced some stiff competition this weekend at the Islander Splash in Corpus Christi.
